  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 6th level, your spores gain the ability to infest a corpse and animate it. If a <strong>beast </strong>or a <strong>humanoid </strong>that is Small or Medium dies within 10 feet of you, you can use your reaction to animate it, causing it to stand up immediately with 1 hit point. The creature uses the <strong>Zombie</strong> stat block in the Monster Manual. It remains animate for 1 hour, after which time it collapses and dies.</p>\n<p>In combat, the zombie's turn comes immediately after yours. It obeys your mental commands, and the only action it can take is the <strong>Attack </strong>action, making one melee attack.</p>\n<p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your <strong>Wisdom modifier</strong> (minimum of once), and you regain all expended uses of it when you finish a <strong>long rest</strong>.</p>",
